fieldvaluepairs.string: Prof. P: What are you doing on tis finest of evenings?
Just finishing up that architecture/parallel work you assigned of course!
Prof. P: That's good. I have something dark to tell you.
Prof. P: When I was a wee little lad I learned a mysterious secret about USF!
Prof. P: There is a secret cavern that lies underneath the school my boy!
Prof. P: However, be warned. There is a unique way to navigate these caverns.
Prof. P: You must use the left and right arrows to move and the up arrow to jump.
Whoa, suddenly I feel tired, I think I drank too much.
